    ComponentCallbacks, SharedPreferences.OnSharedPreferenceChangeListener, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.lifecycle.HasDefaultViewModelProviderFactory, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner, DynamicLifecycle, DynamicSearchListener, DynamicTransitionListener
    public class DynamicPermissionsFragment
extends DynamicFragment
    Base fragment class to show a list of required permissions in a recycler view. It will be used internally by the DynamicPermissionsActivity to request or manage permissions.
